To install mpich2 on laptop:

1. Download the mpi library from http://www.mpich.org/downloads/versions/
Current verion is mpich-3.1.3

2. Extract the tar file.

3. To install:
export "ac_cv_tls=none"
./configure --enable-shared --prefix=/usr/local/mpich2
make
make install

4. You need to include the /usr/local/mpich2/include and one of mpilib in your Makefile - see the Makefile
